OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA dry, bright and chilly
OL,6,Fstart. Remaining mostly dry with cloud
OL,7,Fincreasing from the west. Some light
OL,8,Frain is possible in the west by
OL,9,Fevening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FShowery
OL,12,Frain will move east on Sunday. Cloudy
OL,13,Fon Monday with some rain later.
OL,14,FTurning rather wet and windy on
OL,15,FTuesday. Temperatures slowly
OL,16,Fincreasing near to average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
